[normal]2.[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold] Do authorities take sufficient advantage of collaborative and joint procurement opportunities, including those available from central government? In addition, the Committee would welcome information on PFI contracts and their operation with local government.[bold]&#xa0;
